{"title_page": "Klejdi Hyka", "text_new": "{{short description|Albanian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                 = Klejdi Hyka\n| image                = \n| caption              =\n| fullname             = Klejdi Hyka\n| birth_date           = {{birth date and age|1997|6|13|df=y}}\n| birth_place          = [[Durr\u00ebs]], [[Albania]]\n| height               = {{height|m=}}\n| position             = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub          =\n| clubnumber           = \n| youthyears1          = \n| youthclubs1          = [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta Durr\u00ebs]]\n| years1               = 2015\u20132017\n| clubs1               = [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta]]\n| caps1                = 6\n| goals1               = 0\n| years2               = 2017\n| clubs2               = [[Besa Kavaj\u00eb|Besa]]\n| caps2                = 8\n| goals2               = 1\n| years3               = 2017\u20132018\n| clubs3               = [[KF Korabi Peshkopi|Korabi]]\n| caps3                = 2\n| goals3               = 0\n| nationalyears1       =\n| nationalteam1        = \n| nationalcaps1        = \n| nationalgoals1       = \n| pcupdate             = \n| ntupdate             = 3 February 2018\n}}\n'''Klejdi Hyka''' (born 13 June 1997) is an [[Albania]]n professional [[association football|footballer]] who most recently played for [[KF Korabi Peshkopi|Korabi Peshkopi]] in the [[Albanian First Division]].<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/players/klejdi-hyka/392490/ Soccerway profile]</ref><ref>[http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.klejdi.hyka.249578.en.html Footballdatabase profile]</ref><ref>[http://www.yllpress.com/50024/durresi-doli-fitues-i-kupa-e-pavaresise-ulqini-2012.html Durr\u00ebsi doli fitues i \u201cKupa e Pavar\u00ebsis\u00eb\u201d Ulqini 2012]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hyka, Klejdi}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Durr\u00ebs]]\n[[Cat